reviews.comment: I can take my wife to work on electric, stop for a partial charge to get home and read books from the church library about Unitarian Universalist history while ‘filling up’. I appreciate the solar based charging station. Way to go TJ. I’ll check your Sunday and Open Campus schedules online🎏🙏🌈
Convenience charge, will move if someone else needs charge.

user.about: President of EVolve KY, Kentucky’s electric vehicle organization. Group meets monthly. Visit our website at www.evolveky.org or call me for more information.
